Paper: hep-th/9407016

Date: 1994-07-04

Title: TQFT versus RCFT

Comments: 8 pages + 5 figure pages in PostScript

Journal-ref: Mod.Phys.Lett. A10 (1995) 331-336

A straightforward relationship between the two approaches to 3-dimensionaltopological invariants, one of them put forward by Witten in the framework oftopological quantum field theory, and the second one proposed by Kohno in termsof rational conformal field theory, is established.